            <p class="comment-content">《会饮篇》好 淡定攻和诱受的故事……</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1017651173">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1017651173" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1017651173" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1017651173">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/TongGuanxiong/">童</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-03-04</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">佛陀都已经去世很久了，希腊才出现这种低层次的哲学。人类智慧的差异实在太大了…这本书适合给初中生启蒙看看。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

